### Banking Transactions API - Sample Requests
### Use with IntelliJ HTTP Client or VS Code REST Client

### ===================
### Transaction Endpoints
### ===================

### Create a deposit transaction
POST http://localhost:8080/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Create a withdrawal transaction
POST http://localhost:8080/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 250.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "withdrawal"
}

### Create a transfer transaction
POST http://localhost:8080/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-78901",
  "amount": 500.00,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### Get all transactions
GET http://localhost:8080/transactions

### Get transactions filtered by account
GET http://localhost:8080/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345

### Get transactions filtered by type
GET http://localhost:8080/transactions?type=deposit

### Get transactions filtered by date range
GET http://localhost:8080/transactions?from=2024-01-01&to=2024-12-31

### Get transactions with multiple filters
GET http://localhost:8080/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345&type=transfer&from=2024-01-01

### Get transaction by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/transactions/1

### ===================
### Account Endpoints
### ===================

### Get account balance
GET http://localhost:8080/accounts/ACC-12345/balance

### Get account summary
GET http://localhost:8080/accounts/ACC-12345/summary

### ===================
### Validation Error Examples
### ===================

### Invalid currency code (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "INVALID",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Missing required fields (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Invalid amount - negative (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": -50.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Invalid amount - too many decimal places (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 100.999,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}
